   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "PROBLEM\nAs the context window fills, system-prompt\ninstructions dilute \u2014 the agent starts on-brand and\nends generic.\n\nEXAMPLE\nTurn 1: crisp, professional.  \u2192  Turn 20: vague,\noff-brand, inconsistent.\n\nHOW v4 STOPS IT\nPersona guard: track length + tone, re-inject a\nsystem-prompt summary at intervals, escalate past a\nlength threshold.",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "PROBLEM\nAs the context window fills, system-prompt\ninstructions dilute \u2014 the agent starts on-brand and\nends generic.\n\nEXAMPLE\nTurn 1: crisp, professional.  \u2192  Turn 20: vague,\noff-brand, inconsistent.\n\nHOW v4 STOPS IT\nPersona guard: track length + tone, re-inject a\nsystem-prompt summary at intervals, escalate past a\nlength threshold.",
   "lineHeight": 1.3,
   "baseline": 13
  },
